title: forum and summoner level not syncing
body: I've actually been playing for like a year or two now im level 32 but im only level 5 here?

replies.body: You likely just hadn't posted here since then, and the boards were a little behind in what level you actually were. Looks like posting here pushed through a sync, and I can see you're level 32 now!

Hey there!

That's very odd, it's showing you as level 32 when I hover over your name. Have you tried clearing your cache and cookies to see if that helped?

Let me know!

-Nel
